PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2: Former Army Ranger, author and Pennsylvania senate candidate, Sean Parnell calls in to talk about his combat tour and the US withdrawal from Afghanistan. Biden had to step in and clean up Psaki's mess. Biden Says "Communism Is A ‘Universally Failed System,’ And Socialism Is No ‘Useful Substitute’". Super socialist AOC supports BLM, communist dictatorship, blames Trump-era restrictions on Cuba's failures.
